      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ESPECIAL KAI (2) has a strong record this track and trip with nine wins and seven placings from 20 starts. Recorded a 1.3 lengths win (19.29) in a Free For All last time at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. LADY GUNAI (4) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (19.38) at this track over 350m. Expecting another good run. EVIL EYE (7) ran below best last time finishing fourth (16.95) over 300m at this track in a Free For All. Solid record here at this trip including 16 wins. Has a strong record out of this box with six wins and a minor placing from 10 starts. Likely to be thereabouts. KNEE DEEP (5) placed last time (16.92) at this track in a Free For All, finishing second and beaten half a length. Has three wins already from this draw.",
